                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/evensimple/">阿勺</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-04-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">1.欲闻其声，反默；欲张，反敛；欲高，反下；欲取，反与。2.志者，欲之使也。欲多则心散，心散则志衰，志衰则思不达。(那天翻一翻文言文玩好了）</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="784707744">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-784707744" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-784707744" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="784707744">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
