                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-03-16</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">精彩的战国时代。合纵连横的智慧，谋略和口舌，仍具有很强的借鉴意义。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
